<h1>Trunk Configuration</h1>
<p>The &quot;Trunk Configuration&quot; option of the &quot;Billing&quot; menu allows us to determine which trunks will be used to get the calls for the billing process.</p>
<img src="/images/help_bill_trunk_config_1.png">
<p>The list displays all the registered trunks. You must select which ones will be used for billing and then click on the &quot;Billing Capable&quot; button.</p>
